  <brief_title>Comparing the Consolidation Regimens of IDA With Intermediate-dose Cytarabine Versus Intermediate-dose Cytarabine Alone for Elderly AML Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Comparison of Consolidation Treatment in Elderly Patients With Acute Myeloid Leukemia: Idarubicin (IDA) Combined With Intermediate-dose Cytarabine Versus Intermediate-dose Cytarabine Alone</official_title>
