  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates Idarubicin (IDA) in combination with the intermediate-dose cytarabine,&#xD;
      compared with intermediate-dose cytarabine alone, as a consolidation treatment for elderly&#xD;
      AML in first remission.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
